title: Pledge-A-Paw Dog Walk Event to benefit Camden County Animal Shelter (Camden County, NJ)
text: ( Source : Camden County, NJ ) (October 8, 2015 ) -The Camden County Animal Shelter will be hosting its 2nd Annual Pledge-A-Paw Dog Walk and Event; sponsored by Camden County Board of Freeholders on Sunday, October 11th from 12 p.m. to 4 p.m.
